title: Raw Paws Pet Food Announces $500 in Prizes for Best Pet Halloween Costume Picture
text:
Raw Paws Pet Food
Raw Paws Pet Food announces it's first annual Pet Halloween Contest. It's the ultimate contest where you and your friends decide the winners - see the details below to win $500 in free pet food!
INDIANAPOLIS , Oct. 26, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Raw Paws Pet Food - https://www.rawpawspetfood.com announces the first annual Halloween Pet Costume Contest. $500 in prizes awarded!
Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151026/280501
We have just launched our first annual Halloween Pet Costume Contest. The concept is simple. Just click on this link - https://www.facebook.com/RawPawsPetFood/app_451684954848385
Raw Paws Pet Food is the leader in premium raw pet foods for dogs and cats. We have shipped to thousands of customers nationwide - from our place to your door.
We source from the highest quality farms and USDA inspected facilities to guarantee the best quality meats for the perfect carnivore diet for your cat or dog. Raw Paws also offers the best single ingredient chews and dehydrated treats for hours of snacking pleasure for your pets.
We offer all new and existing customers - Custom Meal Plans at no charge ( $59 value!) to help select the best products for their cats or dogs. We want the best quality foods for our customers' pets - https://www.rawpawspetfood.com/customized-meal-plan-s/349.htm
Raw Paws Pet Food is the leader in eCommerce supply of premium raw, complete diets for cats and dogs. Raw Paws has award winning customer service, and the best quality meats and natural chews and treats delivered from our place directly to your home - www.rawpawspetfood.com . Enter your pet's picture in the best costume you can come up with - then, share your picture with friends. It's a democracy at Raw Paws Pet Food! The picture with the most "votes" wins. There will be a first, second and third place winner.
Good luck everyone! May the best dressed dog or cat win!
To view the original version on PR Newswire, visit: http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/raw-paws-pet-food-announces-500-in-prizes-for-best-pet-halloween-costume-picture-300166066.html
